On July 12, the Shanghai Changning District community owner group issued a notice that the Changning Public Security Bureau will jointly launch the "Green Internet Security Service" with China Telecom.
After the service is launched, if users trigger overseas fraud websites when browsing or searching on the home network, the website will be automatically filtered by the system.
The notice requires users to fill in whether to activate this function in the questionnaire, and whether to activate it is up to the user.
